Arduino Uno Connections:

RTC DS3231 Module:
  VCC → 5V
  GND → GND
  SDA → A4
  SCL → A5

Standard 16x2 LCD:
  RS  → Digital Pin 7
  EN  → Digital Pin 8
  D4  → Digital Pin 9
  D5  → Digital Pin 10
  D6  → Digital Pin 11
  D7  → Digital Pin 12
  RW → GND
  VDD → 5V
  V0  → Middle pin of potentiometer
  A   → 5V (through 220Ω resistor)
  K   → GND

SG90 Servo:
  Signal → Digital Pin 6
  VCC    → 5V
  GND    → GND

LED:
  + → Digital Pin 3 (with 220Ω resistor)
  - → GND

Buzzer:
  + → Digital Pin 4
  - → GND

Button:
  One side → Digital Pin 2
  Other side → GND (with 10kΩ pull-down resistor)

Potentiometer:
  Left → 5V
  Middle → LCD V0
  Right → GND
